OL,3,CReform UK candidate denies knowledge
OL,4,Cof his former boss' bribes
OL,6,FA high-profile Reform UK candidate who
OL,7,Fused to work for a politician who made
OL,8,Fpro-Russian statements in the European
OL,9,FParliament says what his former boss
OL,10,Fdid is "abhorrent" and "a betrayal."
OL,12,FLlyr Powell, Reform UK's candidate in
OL,13,Fthe Caerphilly Senedd byelection,
OL,14,Fworked as a constituency caseworker
OL,15,Ffor Nathan Gill while he was an MEP.
OL,17,FNathan Gill, the former leader of
OL,18,FReform UK in Wales, recently pleaded
OL,19,Fguilty to eight counts of bribery on
OL,20,Fdates between December 6 2018 and July
OL,21,F18 2019.
