OL,3,CReform UK candidate denies knowledge
OL,4,Cof his former boss' bribes
OL,6,FHis political opponents have raised
OL,7,Fquestions about whether Llyr Powell
OL,8,Fknew about the offences at the time.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV Wales' National
OL,11,FCorrespondent Rob Osborne, the Reform
OL,12,FUK candidate categorically denied any
OL,13,Fknowledge of Gill's wrongdoing.
OL,15,FMr Powell said: "I'd imagine it's not
OL,16,Fsomething someone broadcasts. It's an
OL,17,Fabhorrent thing to do, to take money
OL,18,Foff a foreign state when you're an
OL,19,Felected member there to represent the
OL,20,Fpeople.
