OL,6,F"Nathan had two different offices. He
OL,7,Fwas once an MEP and an AM. I left
OL,8,FNathan's MEP office just after 2016,
OL,9,Fafter a colleague fell ill of cancer.
OL,10,FSo I went into work in the Senedd in
OL,11,F2016. Nathan left in 2017 then from
OL,12,Fthe Senedd and my employment with him
OL,13,Fended as I went to work for another
OL,14,Felected member. I was not there during
OL,15,Fthe periods. That have been suggested
OL,16,Fin the papers from what I've read. I
OL,17,Fhave no knowledge of anything at all.
OL,18,FAnd any suggestion otherwise is a lie."
